      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ANGRY FRANKY (8) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by half a length at this track in a handy 19.53 beating Zippi Mustang. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to her name from six starts. Looks to have an edge on most of these. DEMONIC SPIRIT (1) was below best last time but prior to that was narrowly beaten when seventh (24.56) in a Rank Limit - Grade 5 at Bendigo. Well placed here and should do much better. FLYING ADLER (5) has been hard to follow lately, running fifth (24.43) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. DALE'S CORNER (2) is worth a look over a shorter journey this time.",
